💄 Makeup Masterclass by Anjali Grover

🗓️ Date: 11th June 2025

💸 Fee: Absolutely Free

⏰ Timing: 11:00 to 2:00 PM

Venue SCO 13 -14 PUDA MARKET Adjoining SARDARJI DEPARTMENT STORE

✨ Unlock Your Inner Artist with Anjali Grover

Whether you’re a makeup enthusiast eager to refine your skills or someone looking to explore the world of beauty, this masterclass is tailored for you. Join renowned makeup artist Anjali Grover for an immersive session where you’ll:
	•	Learn Professional Techniques: Master the art of flawless base application, contouring, eye makeup, and lip artistry.
	•	Discover Industry Secrets: Gain insights into the latest trends and tips that professionals swear by.
	•	Engage in Live Demonstrations: Watch and learn as Anjali demonstrates step-by-step processes, allowing you to follow along in real-time.
	•	Interactive Q&A Session: Have your questions answered and receive personalized advice to enhance your makeup journey. ￼ ￼

⸻
